<p>Use the SubSift REST API Explorer web page, in conjunction with the <a href="[% site.url %]/api">API documentation</a>, to interactively experiment with the SubSift REST API in a Web 2.0 context. As well as being a useful tool in its own right, the SubSift REST API Explorer demonstrates how to access API methods from an HTML page using JavaScript. Inspect the page source of the demo to see how the code works. Further details of how to use SubSift with JavaScript are covered in API documention section: <a href="[% site.url %]/api/examples-javascript">Examples - JavaScript</a>.</p>

