<h2>ILRT Matcher</h2>

<div>
<a href="[% site.url %]/demo/ilrt_matcher" alt="Demo: ILRT Matcher">
  <img src="[% site.media %]/img/demo/ilrt_matcher.png" style="float: left; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 10px 40px 0px 0;" />
</a>
</div>

<p>Enter keywords or the text of an abstract or article to find the closest matching person in an organisation, based on textual similarity to staff homepages.
The results are displayed as a bar chart, optionally including the list of terms that contribute to the similarity scores.
The organisation in this demo is <a href="http://www.ilrt.bris.ac.uk" class="external">ILRT</a>, but the design pattern is generic.</p>

<p><strong>Demo:</strong> <a href="[% site.url %]/demo/ilrt_matcher">ILRT Matcher</a></p>

