<h2>DBLP Author Finder</h2>

<div>
<a href="[% site.url %]/demo/dblp_search" alt="Demo: DBLP Author Finder">
  <img src="[% site.media %]/img/demo/dblp_search.png" style="float: left; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 10px 40px 0px 0;" />
</a>
</div>

<p>Enter a list of the names of academic authors and search for possible author pages in the <a href="http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/" target="dblp" class="external">DBLP</a> bibliographic database. The purpose of this demo is to make it easy to build lists of urls for bibliographic web pages of potential conference/journal paper reviewers. A bibliographic web page lists the titles of the publications of an academic author and in that sense represents their expertise and interests.</p>

<p><strong>Demo:</strong> <a href="[% site.url %]/demo/dblp_search">DBLP Author Finder</a></p>

